00:26:20,760 --> 00:26:21,640
What do you want?

433
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:23,560
What do you want?

434
00:26:29,070 --> 00:26:29,920
Move aside!

435
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,110
I said I won't move!

436
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:32,880
Come, let's see who's the bigger one!

437
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:35,110
Move!

438
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:46,950
Today is Mr. Zhao's wedding day.

439
00:26:47,350 --> 00:26:48,470
We'll make way,

440
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:50,880
and what harm will that do?

441
00:26:51,390 --> 00:26:54,860
♪The sea surges in silence deep♪

442
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:57,760
♪The waves rise and fall as you lead♪

443
00:26:58,520 --> 00:26:59,680
We can make way,

444
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:01,640
but this excitement

445
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:02,400
cannot be given up!

446
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:02,950
Exactly!

447
00:27:03,430 --> 00:27:04,920
Let me perform a dance for you!

448
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:05,140
♪Burns bright for a promised name♪

449
00:27:05,610 --> 00:27:09,210
♪Love long locked in a hidden place♪

450
00:27:09,210 --> 00:27:12,380
♪Bound by ties too much to erase♪

451
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:15,970
♪Rising and falling together amidst the waves♪

452
00:27:15,970 --> 00:27:21,170
♪Why fear loneliness in the end?♪

453
00:27:21,170 --> 00:27:24,800
♪Year after year♪

454
00:27:24,840 --> 00:27:28,440
♪Just for a fleeting moment to hold dear♪

455
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:31,950
♪Far away, two entwined♪

456
00:27:32,010 --> 00:27:35,480
♪Yet I remain, my shadow behind♪

457
00:27:35,630 --> 00:27:39,180
♪Unforgotten♪

458
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:42,430
♪Memories entwined, stronger than love's song♪

459
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:44,430
♪A lifetime unfolds, a solitary bloom♪

460
00:27:44,430 --> 00:27:45,590
Grandfather promised me

461
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:48,680
if I could secure the title of Brocade Master this time,

462
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:50,710
he'd allow me

463
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,070
to propose to your family.

464
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:53,590
♪I will hold on long♪

465
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:54,160
[Together Forever]

466
00:27:54,190 --> 00:27:55,950
Hasn't been launched yet, and it's already working its magic?

467
00:27:58,920 --> 00:28:00,230
You came here just for me.

468
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:01,520
You're really different.

469
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:03,880
Rising swiftly to the heavens.

470
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,040
Isn't this

471
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:07,000
exactly the person in my heart?

472
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:07,880
He who understands me

473
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,160
is none other than Mr. Zhao.

474
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,860
♪The sky stretches vast, forlorn♪

475
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,920
We've worked so hard for so long,

476
00:28:13,950 --> 00:28:16,160
and finally, we can be together.

477
00:28:16,520 --> 00:28:17,520
