478
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:17,990
♪The wind blows again♪

479
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:21,270
♪You are my anchor, my destined end♪

480
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:24,280
♪Love has no strength to break free♪

481
00:28:24,280 --> 00:28:25,640
Perhaps our emotions

482
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:27,800
aren't as important as you think.

483
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:28,800
♪Even if it ends with no decree♪

484
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:30,280
But abandoning you

485
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:32,710
is my own choice.

486
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,720
[Bride Niu Wuniang, Bridegroom Zhao Xiuyuan]

487
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:35,580
♪Stirring ripples, a whirlpool set free♪

488
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:41,020
♪Year after year♪

489
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:44,070
♪Just for a fleeting moment to hold dear♪

490
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,560
Walk over the mats and bags,

491
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:47,430
wishing for the continuity of generations!

492
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:51,070
Scatter beans to ward off the three misfortunes!

493
00:28:51,070 --> 00:28:51,600
♪Yet I remain, my shadow behind♪

494
00:28:52,470 --> 00:28:55,680
First, for wealth and prosperity!

495
00:28:57,160 --> 00:29:00,470
Second, for gold and jade in abundance!

496
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:04,880
Third, for the three top honors in the imperial exam!

497
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:09,710
Fourth, for dragon and phoenix bringing good fortune!

498
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:14,590
Fifth, for sons becoming ministers!

499
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:15,560
Governor Zhang.

500
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:19,040
Sixth, for thriving in harmony!

501
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:22,070
How come you're here too?

502
00:29:23,190 --> 00:29:24,400
General Niu is here.

503
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,430
Who would dare not come?

504
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:28,310
Look,

505
00:29:28,470 --> 00:29:31,400
half of Yizhou's elite has arrived.

506
00:29:33,280 --> 00:29:37,070
Tenth, for full blessings!

507
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:41,350
The bride steps over the saddle and the balance,

508
00:29:41,470 --> 00:29:43,280
wishing all her desires be fulfilled

509
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:45,350
and for peace and happiness through generations!

510
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:55,230
Looking into the mirror, bow in respect.

511
00:29:58,280 --> 00:29:59,640
Husband and wife, as one,

512
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,760
may all evil be driven away!

513
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,430
Tie the belt together

514
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:14,640
and enter the bridal chamber!

515
00:30:15,710 --> 00:30:16,520
All right,

516
00:30:17,470 --> 00:30:18,640
We no longer need you here.

517
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,430
You may leave now.

518
00:30:24,710 --> 00:30:25,760
Xiuyuan, stay a moment.

519
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:44,920
Congratulations, General Niu!

520
00:30:48,310 --> 00:30:49,110
Esteemed guests,

521
00:30:49,710 --> 00:30:52,560
today, aside from my daughter's wedding joy,

522
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,190
I have another happy event

523
00:30:54,190 --> 00:30:55,520
to share with you all.

524
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:00,040
Everyone, please sit.

525
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,040
Xiuyuan,

526
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:10,350
since everyone's here today,

527
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:12,110
bring out your hard work

528
00:31:12,110 --> 00:31:13,230
and let everyone see.

529
00:31:14,190 --> 00:31:14,920
Got it.

530
00:31:53,230 --> 00:31:54,640
Shu Red outshines

531
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:56,470
all reds

532
00:31:57,010 --> 00:31:58,020
[From Bai Juyi's "The Everlasting Regret"]

533
00:31:58,050 --> 00:31:59,170
and outshines in six palaces the fairest face.

534
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:00,430
What a pity.

535
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:04,070
Since Ji Guinan was punished and died,

536
00:32:04,280 --> 00:32:05,280
Shu Red

537
00:32:05,560 --> 00:32:07,280
has also disappeared.

538
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:08,880
For many years,

539
00:32:08,950 --> 00:32:10,350
the Zhao family

540
00:32:10,470 --> 00:32:14,040
has been determined to revive the glory of Shu Red.

541
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:16,950
Heaven rewards the determined.

542
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:19,110
My grandson, Zhao Xiuyuan,

543
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:23,310
the future head of the Zhao family,

544
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,280
has finally perfected

545
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:28,760
this Shu Red that outshines all reds!

546
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:31,800
Isn't Mr. Zhao in the brocade business?

547
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,560
How did he also learn silk dyeing?

548
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,230
Is it because of Ji Yingying...?

549
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:43,350
You're all veterans of the brocade business.

550
00:32:43,950 --> 00:32:45,110
You've all seen

551
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,190
the unparalleled beauty of Shu Red.

552
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:50,110
Today, I ask you to witness

553
00:32:50,950 --> 00:32:52,350
whether this silk

554
00:32:52,590 --> 00:32:54,230
truly represents real Shu Red.

555
00:32:58,350 --> 00:33:00,160
